This example shows a litte car shop.

Functionality

User:
- add / edit user to the shop (admin rights expected)
- users can be seller or customer
- each user can be admin
- user list / edit / add not linked (url: /admin/userList.xhtml)

Car
Seller
- add / edit three types of cars (normal, cabrio, pickup)
Customer
- display car details
- oder car --> select payment cash or creditcard

general
- shop is secured via spring security 3

installation
The requiered frameworks should be loaded via maven the requiered pom.xml file is included.
The database should be set up with the help of the sql.sql file in /database/. (example data included)

